channel.title: Getting My Server Up - Help
channel.description:
Hi, I'm Aiden,I needed some help on getting my server up. I have most of it ok. It won't load my mopar for it. I am using AdventureScape. The command prompt says:[code]AdventureScape Is Starting Up With Port 0.0.0.0:43594[/code]
Then it just stops. What do I do?
[glow=red,2,300]Thanks if you help me![/glow]
